[55.82, "o", "\r\n"]
[55.82, "o", "\u001b[1;36m\u2501\u2501\u2501 Step 4: The fix \u2014 collector sidecar inside the Kata VM \u2501\u2501\u2501\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[59.32, "o", "\r\n"]
[59.32, "o", "A second RHACS collector runs as a privileged sidecar\r\n"]
[59.42, "o", "inside the Kata pod. It attaches core_bpf probes to the\r\n"]
[59.52, "o", "guest kernel and sends events to the RHACS sensor.\r\n"]
